WEBVTT

00:01.935 --> 00:03.268
<i>Previously on"Salem"...</i>

00:06.339 --> 00:07.840
No.

00:08.842 --> 00:09.842
I'm sorry.

00:13.014 --> 00:14.947
She deserves it.
But the innocent life

00:14.949 --> 00:16.515
inside her womb does not!

00:16.517 --> 00:17.983
That you spared me.

00:17.985 --> 00:19.952
I know which one I want. Mercy.

00:19.954 --> 00:21.854
She keeps their manhoods
locked up in her room.

00:21.856 --> 00:23.455
Go back. Go.

00:24.525 --> 00:25.657
Aah!

00:25.659 --> 00:27.226
- Who did this?
- Drink it,

00:27.228 --> 00:29.395
and you, too, shall be free
of my hold forever.

00:29.397 --> 00:31.296
I do not want it.

00:31.298 --> 00:33.832
I have earned my reward
and my vengeance.

00:33.834 --> 00:35.667
All shall be as we agreed.

00:35.669 --> 00:38.637
Once you arrange this
one last matter.

00:38.639 --> 00:41.040
Murder my brother.

00:41.042 --> 00:42.875
There's one with child.
Will you have a look?

00:42.877 --> 00:44.676
I need to find him.

00:44.678 --> 00:46.378
The baby's father?

00:46.380 --> 00:48.414
Cotton Mather.

