00:58.391 --> 01:00.893
This is too nice for a wh...

01:02.162 --> 01:04.997
- For someone like me.
- Nonsense.

01:04.998 --> 01:08.033
This is now your room,
for as long as you need it.

01:08.035 --> 01:10.903
What will your father say?

01:10.905 --> 01:14.006
My parents passed away
during the plague.

01:14.008 --> 01:16.008
I'm so sorry.

01:20.180 --> 01:24.636
They're with the lord now,
and I can use their name

01:24.787 --> 01:28.854
and their fortune to help the
less fortunate in Salem.

01:28.856 --> 01:31.890
You were always so different

01:31.892 --> 01:33.959
from everyone else in this town.

01:33.961 --> 01:37.729
So kind, so generous,

01:37.731 --> 01:39.798
even to a fallen woman.

01:42.469 --> 01:45.537
In this world,
no woman should judge another

01:45.539 --> 01:48.033
for the choices she's
forced to make.

01:48.184 --> 01:50.642
And I'm quite sure
we are all fallen

01:50.644 --> 01:55.744
in one way or another. But when
we fall, we get back up.

01:56.746 --> 02:00.415
