01:59.320 --> 02:02.087
You need to get some rest,
Gloriana,

02:02.089 --> 02:04.456
and look after yourself,

02:04.458 --> 02:06.258
and most important of all,

02:06.260 --> 02:10.128
the precious cargo of life
you now carry.

02:10.131 --> 02:13.002
Every life is precious,
but I can't help feeling

02:13.153 --> 02:15.851
the little babe in your
womb is especially so.

